---
import Bi from '../shared/Bi.astro';
import Callout from '../shared/Callout.astro';
import Section from '../mechanics/Section.astro';
---
<Section id="early-game" titleZh="第 3 階段：開首都 + 周邊偵察" titleEn="Phase 3: Land your capital, scout neighbours" eyebrow="Lumi §4.1">
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="第 2 村開了之後，下一個關鍵決策：哪個位置當「真正的首都」（即放皇宮 / 升 Lv11+ 田的地方）。原則："
      en="With village #2 settled, the next critical decision: where to plant your real capital (the village that gets the Palace and Lv11+ fields). Principles:"
    />
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><Bi zh="優先找 15c（1-1-1-15）或 9c（3-3-3-9）的田地" en="Prioritize 15c (1-1-1-15) or 9c (3-3-3-9) field layouts" /></li>
    <li><Bi zh="周圍最好有糧食 +50% 綠洲" en="Look for crop +50% oases nearby" /></li>
    <li><Bi zh="不要太遠：跟你的 feeder 村距離 ≤60 格（所需商人數取決於部族和距離，請用商路計算器精算）" en="Don't go too far: keep ≤60 fields from your feeders (merchants needed depends on tribe + distance; use the Trade Route calculator for precise count)" /></li>
  </ul>

  <h3><Bi zh="每村開始辦慶典（≈ Day 7+）" en="Start celebrations in every village (~Day 7+)" /></h3>
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="當被動 CP 加上每日慶典 CP 足以回本城鎮廳的投資時，就值得升城鎮廳並開始連續慶典。CP 是擴張燃料，越早累積越好。"
      en="Once passive CP + daily celebration CP justifies the Town Hall investment, build Town Hall and start running celebrations back-to-back. CP is the expansion fuel — accumulate aggressively."
    />
  </p>

  <h3><Bi zh="檢查 20×20 範圍內的玩家" en="Scout your 20×20 neighbourhood" /></h3>
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="早期最大的危險是「短行軍時間」—— 鄰居走 30 分鐘就到你家。打開遊戲內地圖，列出周圍：誰開村快？誰有 OFF 點數？誰可能是大號／sitter？需要時派偵察兵看他兵種。發現危險立刻通知你的聯盟領袖。"
      en="Early-game's biggest threat is short marching distance — a neighbour might be 30 minutes away. Open the in-game map and list the people around you: who is settling fast? Who has OFF points? Who might be a big account or a sitter? Scout when needed. Tell your alliance lead the moment you spot a threat."
    />
  </p>

  <Callout kind="tip" titleZh="不要把 spawn 村變成主錘子" titleEn="Don't turn your spawn into your main hammer">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="Spawn 村太顯眼，敵人看得到；而且 spawn 一般是 4-4-4-6 田，糧食不夠養大軍。錘子應該放在 v3+（從 cap 開出去的村），位置自選。"
        en="Spawns are visible to everyone, and 4-4-4-6 fields can't feed a large army. Build your hammer in village #3 or later (settled from your cap), in a hidden spot of your choosing."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>
</Section>
